'''波特拉奇河'''（{{lang-en|Potlatch River}}）是一條位於[[美國|美國]][[愛達荷州|愛達荷州]]的河流，長約{{convert|56|mi|km}}<ref name="gnis"/>。波特拉奇河為清水河的支流，而清水河是[[斯內克河|斯內克河]]的支流，後者則是[[哥倫比亞河|哥倫比亞河]]最大的支流<ref name="Potlatch River Plan">{{Cite web |url = http://www.latahsoil.com/sitebuildercontent/sitebuilderfiles/PotlatchRiverManagementPlanCompleteOct2007.pdf |title = Potlatch River Watershed Management Plan |author = Resource Planning Unlimited |year = 2007 |language = en |accessdate = 2020-09-02 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110713185000/http://www.latahsoil.com/sitebuildercontent/sitebuilderfiles/PotlatchRiverManagementPlanCompleteOct2007.pdf |archivedate = 2011-07-13}}</ref>。河流毗鄰洛磯山脈的西山麓，曾被[[哥倫比亞高原|哥倫比亞高原]]的乾旱草原所圍繞。現時河流主要用於農業灌溉。

波特拉奇河的名稱源於「[[散財宴|散財宴]]」（{{lang-en|Potlatch}}），是[[太平洋西北地區|太平洋西北地區]][[美洲原住民|美洲原住民]]的一種贈禮儀式，而這些原住民部落在移居者到達河流前便已在此生活了數百年{{sfn|Oregon Historical Society|1948|p=52}}<ref name="Idaho DES"/>。19世紀後期，拓荒者移居至波特拉奇河流域，並建立了農場和牧場。在伐木業及農業並未興起前，河流流域曾經長著種類繁多的河岸和森林植物，亦有不同種類的魚類在此生活。此後，過度[[伐木|伐木]]導致流域內的大部份森林消失，而現時河流生態仍在恢復中。

== 流向及流域 ==
波特拉奇河發源自愛達荷州中北部的{{tsl|en|Hoodoo Mountains|胡都山脈}}<ref name="Mineral Resources">{{Cite web |url = https://www.idahogeology.org/PDF/County_Reports_(C)/C-2.pdf |title = Mineral Resources of Latah County |last = Hubbard |first = Charles R. |year = 1957 |publisher = Idaho Bureau of Mines and Geology |language = en |accessdate = 2020-09-02 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110930230749/https://www.idahogeology.org/PDF/County_Reports_(C)/C-2.pdf |archivedate = 2011-09-30}}</ref>。河流主要往西南方向流動，橫越位於洛磯山脈附近的哥倫比亞高原東部地區<ref name="Potlatch Report 06-08">{{Cite web |url = http://nptwaterresources.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Potlatch_River_Water_Quality_Monitoring_Report_2006_2007.pdf |title = Potlatch River Monitoring Report 2006-2008 |last = Clark |first = Ken |year = 2010 |publisher = Idaho Association of Soil Conservation Districts |language = en |accessdate = 2020-09-02 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200902145314/http://nptwaterresources.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Potlatch_River_Water_Quality_Monitoring_Report_2006_2007.pdf |archivedate = 2020-09-02}}</ref>。在[[愛達荷狹地|愛達荷狹地]]南部，波特拉奇河的兩條分汊形成了河源：位於拉塔縣的波特拉奇河西汊（West Fork Potlatch River）以及位於清水縣的波特拉奇河東汊（East Fork Potlatch River）<ref name="Potlatch Report 06-08"/>。這兩條分汊在[[赫爾默_(愛達荷州)|赫爾默]]附近匯合，之後河水便流進峽谷並一直延伸到河口<ref name="Potlatch Report 06-08"/>。在峽谷內，波特拉奇河先後與松溪（Pine Creek）、大熊溪（Big Bear Creek）、中波特拉奇溪（Middle Potlatch Creek）、小波特拉奇溪（Little Potlatch Creek）、博爾德河（Boulder Creek）及錫達溪（Cedar Creek）合流<ref name="Annual Report 2007">{{Cite web |url = https://collaboration.idfg.idaho.gov/FisheriesTechnicalReports/Res08-139Bowersox2007%20Potlatch%20River%20Steelhead%20Monitoring%20and%20Evaluation%20Annual%20Report.pdf |title = Potlatch River Strrlhead Monitoring and Evaluation Annual Report 2007 |last = Bowersox |first = Brett |year = 2008 |publisher = Idaho Department of Fish and Game |language = en |accessdate = 2020-09-02 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161228092908/https://collaboration.idfg.idaho.gov/FisheriesTechnicalReports/Res08-139Bowersox2007%20Potlatch%20River%20Steelhead%20Monitoring%20and%20Evaluation%20Annual%20Report.pdf |archivedate = 2016-12-28}}</ref>。[[3號愛達荷州州道|3號愛達荷州州道]]與一部分較低的峽谷平行著，而[[朱麗埃塔_(愛達荷州)|朱麗埃塔]]則位於中波特拉奇溪與河流的匯合處。河流最終在[[斯波爾丁_(愛達荷州)|斯波爾丁]]及默特爾（Myrtle）之間與清水河合流<ref name="Idaho DES">{{Cite web |url = http://www.deq.state.id.us/water/data_reports/surface_water/tmdls/potlatch_river/potlatch_river_entire.pdf |title = Potlatch River Subbasin Assessment and TMDLs |author = Idaho Department of Environmental Quality |year = 2008 |language = en |accessdate = 2020-09-02 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20091002012628/http://www.deq.state.id.us/water/data_reports/surface_water/tmdls/potlatch_river/potlatch_river_entire.pdf |archivedate = 2009-10-02}}</ref>，而匯合處的海拔高度約為{{convert|801|ft|m}}<ref name="gnis"/>。

根據美國地質調查局的數據，河口流量的平均速率為{{convert|379.8|ft3/s|m³/s}}<ref name="Waterdata Report">{{Cite web |url = https://waterdata.usgs.gov/usa/nwis/uv?13341570 |title = USGS 133341570 Potlatch River |author = National Water Information System |publisher = U.S. Geological Survey |language = en |accessdate = 2020-09-02 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200902150500/https://waterdata.usgs.gov/usa/nwis/uv?13341570 |archivedate = 2020-09-02}}</ref>。河流的流量會在冬季和初春時達到最高峰，而夏季和秋季則會下降<ref name="Idaho DES"/>。河流主要流經粗糙的哥倫比亞河玄武岩（哥倫比亞高原亦由其組成），其地質與流經[[華盛頓州|華盛頓州]]及愛達荷州的{{tsl|en|Palouse River|帕盧斯河}}類似<ref name="USGS_Volcanoes">{{Cite web |url = http://vulcan.wr.usgs.gov/LivingWith/Historical/LewisClark/volcanoes_lewis_clark_october_07_1805.html |title = On the Clearwater - Canoe Camp to the Potlatch River |author = United States Geological Survey |language = en |accessdate = 2020-09-03 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110612041856/http://vulcan.wr.usgs.gov/LivingWith/Historical/LewisClark/volcanoes_lewis_clark_october_07_1805.html |archivedate = 2011-06-12}}</ref>。

== 歷史 ==
早在在拓荒者抵達波特拉奇河之前，其中一支美洲原住民部落[[內茲珀斯人|內茲珀斯人]]便已在此生活了數百年<ref name="Idaho DES"/>。河流位於乾旱的哥倫比亞高原東部邊緣，部份地區曾是一片廣闊的乾旱草原，並被森林茂密的山脈圍繞。另外，由於河流位於洛磯山脈的西南方，故波特拉奇河的降雨量相較其他位於西邊的河流（如帕盧斯河及圖坎嫩河）為多。在1805至1806年的[[路易斯與克拉克遠征|路易斯與克拉克遠征]]時，遠征隊沿著清水河順流而下並穿越了波特拉奇河河口{{sfn|Wheeler|1904|p=122}}，但不能確定他們是否最早抵達該處的白人<ref name="USGS_Volcanoes"/>。當時遠征隊稱河流為「一條大溪」，並把其命名為庫爾特溪（{{lang|en|Colter's Creek}}），以紀念遠征隊的其中一名成員{{tsl|en|John Colter|約翰·庫爾特}}{{sfn|Wheeler|1904|p=122}}<ref name="lewis-clark">{{Cite web |url = https://www.lewis-clark.org/article/2613 |title = John Colter |author = Lewis and Clark Trail Heritage Foundation |language = en |accessdate = 2020-09-03 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20191224221540/https://www.lewis-clark.org/article/2613 |archivedate = 2019-12-24}}</ref>。1897年，美國政府把河流改為現時所使用的的名稱<ref name="gnis"/><ref name="lewis-clark"/>。

1870年代，大量拓荒者陸續抵達愛達荷州西部，加上清水河北岸[[奧羅菲諾|奧羅菲諾]]附近的金礦亦吸引了不少的礦工，導致河流及鄰近地區開始出現變化<ref name="Idaho DES"/>。大多數移居者都在河流周邊的草原上建立乾耕農場及牧場。隨著河水往南流經河流流域，土壤條件通常會得到改善，但是河流南部流域在種植農作物上有一個主要弊端：缺水<ref name="Potlatch River Plan"/>。由於河流的流量低，而且河水流經的峽谷非常陡峭，令農民無法引導河水至農場<ref name="Potlatch River Plan"/>。因此，農民只能種植一些不需要灌溉的農作物，而其他無法獲得足夠[[農業用水|農業用水]]的土地則淪為牧場或生產乾草的設施<ref name="Potlatch River Plan"/>。

起初，河流流域內的森林並沒有因為大量拓荒者抵達而受到嚴重影響，但在20世紀初他們開始進行伐木作業後，流域內大部份的[[原始森林|原始森林]]都被清除了<ref name="Potlatch River Plan"/>。後來，拓荒者們建造了區內首間鋸木廠，向當地居民提供木材以供建造房屋和穀倉等設施，但不久之後{{tsl|en|Washington, Idaho and Montana Railway|華盛頓、愛達荷及蒙大納鐵路}}把路線延伸到這地區，令鋸木廠能出口木材至其他地區<ref name="lumbering">{{Cite web |url = http://www.clearwatertribune.com/Special%20Feature/Lumbering.htm |title = Lumbering an economic mainstay in Clearwater County for almost a century |author = 20th Century Chronicles |publisher = Clearwater Tribune |language = en |accessdate = 2020-09-03 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://archive.is/20061109001920/http://www.clearwatertribune.com/Special%20Feature/Lumbering.htm |archivedate = 2013-09-28}}</ref>。雖然伐木業是一個非常有利可圖的行業，但這對波特拉奇河流域的生態持續造成負面影響<ref name="Potlatch River Plan"/><ref name="lumbering"/>。為了開發木材資源，當地居民建造了不少設施，例如防洪壩、滑槽、滑道、[[鐵路支線|鐵路支線]]及小型的蒸汽動力裝置等<ref name="lumbering"/>。可是，在修建鐵路[[路堤|路堤]]及支線時河道被人為拉直，而附近的貧瘠山坡上侵蝕急劇增加，導致許多溪流變得更為淤塞<ref name="Potlatch River Plan"/><ref name="lumbering"/>。現時流域內的原始森林幾乎都已經消失，剩下的大部分是[[次生林|次生林]]<ref name="Potlatch River Plan"/>。

== 生態 ==
波特拉奇河沿岸生長著不少的三角葉楊、顫楊、楓樹以及榿木，而部分小型支流的沿岸則生長著[[山楂屬|山楂屬]]及[[山梅花屬|山梅花屬]]植物<ref name="Idaho DES"/>。另外，在流域內的山麓地區有一大片草原，長滿了黑山楂、針葉樹及[[毛核木屬|毛核木屬]]植物等，更有紀錄指該處一度長滿了愛達荷狐草及藍叢麥草<ref name="Idaho DES"/>。一些霞花屬及闊葉草本植物亦會在波特拉奇河及其支流附近的季節性濕地上出現<ref name="Potlatch River Plan"/>。流域內的森林以[[花旗松|花旗松]]及[[西黃松|西黃松]]為主，亦有少部份如巨冷杉、[[美西側柏|美西側柏]]、西部白松及落葉松生長，而底層則生長著[[風箱果屬|風箱果屬]]及[[唐棣屬|唐棣屬]]等灌木植物<ref name="Idaho DES"/>。河流流域不時有[[山火|山火]]發生，但這亦有利樹林生態發展。在人為干預後，植物群落仍然存在但數量變得較少，而大部分草原亦被農業所清除<ref name="Potlatch River Plan"/>。河流的年均降水量為15至50英吋（380至1,270毫米），而溫度的年均變化約為25至100°F（−4至38°C）<ref name="Potlatch River Plan"/>。

根據{{tsl|en|Idaho Department of Fish and Game|愛達荷州魚類及獵物部}}在2003年至2004年的一項研究，波特拉奇河流域有著13種不同的魚類，包括[[小點吻鱥|小點吻鱥]]、[[吻鱥|吻鱥]]、[[虹鱒|虹鱒]]、[[美洲紅點鮭|美洲紅點鮭]]、[[大口黑鱸|大口黑鱸]]、[[駝背太陽魚|駝背太陽魚]]、{{tsl|en|Sculpin|杜父魚}}及[[黃鱸|黃鱸]]等<ref name="IDFG Report03-04">{{Cite web |url = https://research.idfg.idaho.gov/Fisheries%20Research%20Reports/Volume%20151_Article%2002.pdf |title = Potlatch River Basin—Fisheries Inventory |last = Bowersox |first = Brett |last2 = Brindza |first2 = Nathan |year = 2006 |publisher = Idaho Department of Fish and Game |language = en |accessdate = 2020-09-02 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100110160624/https://research.idfg.idaho.gov/Fisheries%20Research%20Reports/Volume%20151_Article%2002.pdf |archivedate = 2010-01-10}}</ref>。虹鱒及硬頭鱒的[[洄游|洄游]]一度被[[斯內克河|斯內克河]]及[[哥倫比亞河|哥倫比亞河]]下游大壩建設工程所影響<ref name="IDFG Report03-04"/>。這兩種魚在波特拉奇河流域內是最大的魚類種群，其中硬頭鱒佔群落生物量58.4%<ref name="IDFG Report03-04"/>。研究過程期間，科研人員在河流流域的所有溪流內採樣，發現波特拉奇河西汊維持了相對原始的狀態，因此生物多樣性較其他溪流為高，相反波特拉奇河的下游地區則受到農業污水的污染<ref name="IDFG Report03-04"/>。愛達荷州魚類及獵物部後來推行了波特拉奇河硬頭鱒監測和評估計劃（Potlatch River Steelhead Monitoring and Evaluation Program），旨在記錄流域內的硬頭鱒（虹鱒）種群數量<ref name="PRSME 2011">{{Cite web |url = https://collaboration.idfg.idaho.gov/FisheriesTechnicalReports/mgt12-108Bowersox2011%20Potlatch%20River%20Steelhead%20Monitoring%20and%20Evaluation%20Project%202011.pdf |title = POTLATCH RIVER STEELHEAD MONITORING AND EVALUATION - Annual Performance Report 2011 |last = Bowersox |first = Brett J. |last2 = Banks |first2 = Ryan |last3 = Davids |first3 = Nick |year = 2011 |publisher = Idaho Department of Fish and Game |language = en |accessdate = 2020-09-03 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170131073329/https://collaboration.idfg.idaho.gov/FisheriesTechnicalReports/mgt12-108Bowersox2011%20Potlatch%20River%20Steelhead%20Monitoring%20and%20Evaluation%20Project%202011.pdf |archivedate = 2017-01-31}}</ref>。在2010年的野外季節期間，統計人員在上游及下游分別錄得了71隻及252隻成年硬頭鱒，並在整個河流流域錄得了1,230隻亞成體硬頭鱒<ref name="PRSME 2011"/>。另外，在整個流域內的魚苗及幼年硬頭魚的密度分別為0.14條/每百平方米及1.35條/每百平方米<ref name="PRSME 2011"/>。據估計，每年大約有超過1,000條成年硬頭鱒洄游至波特拉奇河<ref name="PRSME 2011"/>，而從波特拉奇河東汊及大熊溪遷出的硬頭鱒數目分別約為6,976條及9,491條<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.clearwaterflycasters.com/newsletter/january2009-tippet.pdf |title = Production, productivity, and life history characteristics of steelhead, Oncorhynchus mykiss, in the Potlatch River drainage, Idaho |author = Bowersox |first = Kent |year = 2009 |publisher = The Tippet |language = en |accessdate = 2020-09-03 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110708163735/http://www.clearwaterflycasters.com/newsletter/january2009-tippet.pdf |archivedate = 2011-07-08 }}</ref>。除了上述的監測計劃外，愛達荷州魚類及獵物部也在2009年推行了一系列七個計劃，以保護波特拉奇河的魚類棲息地<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://fishandgame.idaho.gov/cms/about/compass/direction09.pdf |title = Direction 2009: Issues, Accomplishments, & Priorities |author = The Compass |year = 2009 |publisher = Idaho Department of Fish and Game |language = en |accessdate = 2020-09-03 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100107021022/http://fishandgame.idaho.gov/cms/about/compass/direction09.pdf |archivedate = 2010-01-07}}</ref>。

在波特拉奇河流域內，大約57%的土地被森林覆蓋，而約38%則用於農業和牧場<ref name="Nez Perce">{{Cite web |url = http://www.nezperceswcd.org/Watersheds/ClearwaterRiver/PotlatchRiver.aspx |title = Potlatch River |author = Nez Perce Soil and Water Conservation District |language = en |accessdate = 2020-09-03 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20191025003612/http://www.nezperceswcd.org/Watersheds/ClearwaterRiver/PotlatchRiver.aspx |archivedate = 2019-10-25}}</ref>。其中78%的土地屬於私人擁有，14%的土地屬於[[美國國家森林|美國國家森林]]，7%的土地屬於愛達荷州，其餘則屬於[[美國內政部土地管理局|美國內政部土地管理局]]及[[印第安事務局|印第安事務局]]<ref name="Nez Perce"/><ref>{{Cite web |url = http://nptwaterresources.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Potlatch-River-Subbasin-TMDL-Implementation-Plan-for-Agriculture.pdf |title = Potlatch River Subbasin |author = Idaho Soil Conservation Commission |year = 2010 |publisher = Idaho Department of Environmental Quality |language = en |accessdate = 2020-09-03 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200903145843/http://nptwaterresources.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Potlatch-River-Subbasin-TMDL-Implementation-Plan-for-Agriculture.pdf |archivedate = 2020-09-03}}</ref>。

== 休閒 ==
波特拉奇河流域內的部份山林地區屬於美國國家森林，而在河流上游亦有數個由[[美國國家森林局|美國國家森林局]]管控的露營營地<ref name="USFS_Potlatch">{{Cite web |url = http://www.fs.fed.us/r1/clearwater/fish/rivers/potlatch.htm |title = Potlatch River |author = U.S. Forest Service |language = en |accessdate = 2020-09-04 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121016051003/http://www.fs.fed.us/r1/clearwater/fish/rivers/potlatch.htm |archivedate = 2012-10-16}}</ref>。另外，在河流上游與穆斯溪的匯合處以及河流東汊是可以合法地進行釣魚活動的，但釣魚人士只能釣獲美洲紅點鮭、[[克拉克大麻哈魚|克拉克大麻哈魚]]、硬頭鱒及虹鱒<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://fishandgame.idaho.gov/fish/rules/clear.pdf |title = Clearwater Region |author = Idaho Department of Fish and Game |language = en |accessdate = 2020-09-04 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100130002800/http://fishandgame.idaho.gov/fish/rules/clear.pdf |archivedate = 2010-01-30}}</ref>。愛達荷州魚類及獵物部每年均會把魚苗放入河內，以維持生態平衡<ref name="USFS_Potlatch"/>。

